The Block Australia Fans vs Faves Series 8 Episode 27

The Block is back with a Fans versus Favorites format - will the old hands prevail?

The Block Unlocked Week 4

Join Shelley Craft for all the best behind the scenes from bedroom week on The Block. Judges Neale, Shaynna and Darren give us their thoughts on the completed rooms and we check on progress for Sunday night's delivery of the bathrooms.
